unittitle_ssm: James A. Kelly collection of Brooklyn firefighting records
abstract_ssm: The collection represents a portion of the material generated by several Brooklyn and Kings County volunteer fire companies and by related local, county, state, and national organizations, between 1825 and 1949. The bulk of the material spans the time period between 1850 and 1900.
